# ===============================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ===============================================

# Common issues and solutions:

# 1. Contract interaction failures:
#    - Verify contract addresses are correct
#    - Ensure you're connected to Sepolia testnet
#    - Check your wallet has sufficient ETH for gas

# 2. RPC connection issues:
#    - Verify Infura/Alchemy API key is valid
#    - Check rate limits haven't been exceeded
#    - Try alternative RPC providers if needed

# 3. Wallet connection problems:
#    - Ensure WalletConnect Project ID is configured
#    - Clear browser cache and wallet permissions
#    - Try different wallet providers

# 4. Price feed issues:
#    - Verify Chainlink price feed addresses
#    - Check if feeds are active on Sepolia
#    - Fallback to alternative price sources if needed

# For more help, check the documentation or join our community Discord.
